1.) Add Neuros.TV theme (attached to this bug) by navigating to Tools > 
Add-ons
> Themes, then dragging the .jar file into the left pane of the dialog.
2.) Remove Stop and Reload from URL bar (right-click on an icon, choose
Customize, and drag the Stop and Reload icons from the main window's URL 
bar
into the dialog window)
3.) Remove Bookmarks toolbar: navigate to View > Toolbars and uncheck 
Bookmarks
toolbar
4.) Copy attached neurostv.xml to
~/.mozilla/firefox/*.default/searchplugins/neurostv.xml (permissions 
644). 
Create searchplugins directory if necessary.
5.) Launch Firefox, click the Google search icon, and change it to 
Neuros.TV. 
Ensure the browser is full-screened (F11) and close it.

